[src:mid-air-collision/aeroflot-accidents-and-incidents] Water entered the fuselage and the aircraft broke in three and came to rest.
[src:mid-air-collision/aeroflot-accidents-and-incidents] Following an uneventful flight from Yerevan, the aircraft was on approach when the pilot requested a straight-in approach, which was against procedure that request a circuit vertical to the airport.
